Reasoning: The paper discusses the use of 3D imaging technologies and computer algorithms for image-based modeling of biological control, which suggests a strong focus on computer vision (cs.CV) and biomedical engineering (cs.BM). The paper also mentions the solution of systems of partial differential equations (PDEs), which falls under computational engineering (cs.CE) and mathematical modeling (cs.MS). Finally, the study of morphogenesis and embryonic development falls under the subfield of theoretical and computational biology (q-bio.TO).
